<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Lahore Air Quality Intelligence Report · 2019–2023</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --ink: #0f1117;
  --ink-2: #1c2030;
  --ink-3: #252a3a;
  --rule: #2e3348;
  --mid: #404766;
  --dim: #6b7494;
  --body: #9ba4c0;
  --text: #cdd3e8;
  --bright: #eef0f8;
  --white: #f8f9fc;

  --fire: #ff5733;
  --fire-dim: rgba(255,87,51,0.12);
  --fire-border: rgba(255,87,51,0.3);
  --gold: #e8b84b;
  --gold-dim: rgba(232,184,75,0.1);
  --teal: #38c9b0;
  --teal-dim: rgba(56,201,176,0.1);
  --blue: #4a8ff5;
  --blue-dim: rgba(74,143,245,0.1);
  --purple: #9b74e8;

  --good: #38c9b0;
  --moderate: #e8b84b;
  --sensitive: #f07830;
  --unhealthy: #e84848;
  --veryunhealthy: #9b74e8;
  --hazardous: #c0392b;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: var(--body);
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  min-height: 100vh;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* ===== NOISE OVERLAY ===== */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* ===== HEADER ===== */
header {
  position: relative;
  padding: 5rem 5vw 4rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  overflow: hidden;
  z-index: 1;
}

.header-glow {
  position: absolute;
  top: -120px; right: -100px;
  width: 700px; height: 700px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(255,87,51,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.header-glow-2 {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -200px; left: 20%;
  width: 600px; height: 400px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(74,143,245,0.04) 0%, transparent 65%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.eyebrow {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.eyebrow-line {
  width: 28px; height: 1px;
  background: var(--fire);
}
.eyebrow-text {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  color: var(--fire);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1.1;
  max-width: 720px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
h1 .year {
  display: block;
  color: var(--fire);
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 400;
}

.header-byline {
  margin-top: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--dim);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  max-width: 580px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.meta-strip {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  width: fit-content;
}
.meta-item {
  padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}
.meta-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.meta-item .ml { display: block; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.meta-item .mv { color: var(--text); font-size: 0.7rem; }
.meta-item.warn .mv { color: var(--fire); }

/* ===== MAIN ===== */
main {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 4rem 5vw 8rem;
}

section { margin-bottom: 5rem; }

/* ===== SECTION HEADERS ===== */
.sh {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.sh-num {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--fire);
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding-top: 0.5rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 40px;
}
.sh-body {}
.sh-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.65rem;
  color: var(--bright);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.sh-desc {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--dim);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* ===== KPI GRID ===== */
.kpi-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
@media (max-width: 1100px) { .kpi-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .kpi-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

.kpi {
  padding: 1.6rem 1.4rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  position: relative;
  transition: background 0.25s;
}
.kpi:last-child { border-right: none; }
.kpi:hover { background: var(--ink-2); }
.kpi::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: transparent;
  transition: background 0.25s;
}
.kpi:hover::before { background: var(--fire); }

.kpi-lbl {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mid);
  margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
}
.kpi-val {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
}
.kpi-sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.pill {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.12rem 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  border-radius: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.pill-r { background: rgba(232,72,72,0.14); color: #f87171; border: 1px solid rgba(232,72,72,0.2); }
.pill-o { background: rgba(232,184,75,0.12); color: #fcd34d; border: 1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.2); }
.pill-g { background: rgba(56,201,176,0.12); color: #5eead4; border: 1px solid rgba(56,201,176,0.2); }
.pill-p { background: rgba(155,116,232,0.12); color: #c4b5fd; border: 1px solid rgba(155,116,232,0.2); }

/* ===== CHARTS ===== */
.chart-card {
  background: var(--ink-2);
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 2rem 2rem 1.5rem;
}
.chart-hd { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.chart-hd h3 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--bright);
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
}
.chart-hd p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--dim); }
.chart-wrap { position: relative; width: 100%; }

.chart-legend {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.8rem 1.4rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--dim);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.cl-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
.cl-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.cl-line { width: 18px; height: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.cl-dash { width: 18px; height: 1px; flex-shrink: 0; background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, currentColor 0, currentColor 3px, transparent 3px, transparent 6px); }

.two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--rule);
}
@media (max-width: 800px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.alert {
  background: rgba(232,184,75,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.2);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--body);
}
.alert strong { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }

/* ===== YEAR TABLE ===== */
.data-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.data-table th {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mid);
  padding: 0.75rem 1.2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  text-align: left;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.data-table td {
  padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  font-size: 0.83rem;
  color: var(--body);
}
.data-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.data-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); }
.data-table td.num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; }
.data-table td.warn { color: #fbbf24; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; }
.data-table td.danger { color: #f87171; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; }
.data-table td.ok { color: var(--teal); font-size: 0.78rem; }

/* ===== CORRELATIONS ===== */
.corr-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.corr-lbl {
  width: 150px; flex-shrink: 0;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.67rem;
  color: var(--dim);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.corr-track {
  flex: 1; height: 4px;
  background: var(--ink-3);
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.corr-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; }
.corr-val {
  width: 44px; text-align: right;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.67rem;
  color: var(--text);
}

/* ===== MISSING DATA (SVG ICONS) ===== */
.missing-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--rule);
}
@media (max-width: 1000px) { .missing-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .missing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.missing-card {
  background: var(--ink-2);
  padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem;
  position: relative;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.missing-card:hover { background: var(--ink-3); }

.mc-icon {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--fire);
  opacity: 0.75;
}
.mc-title {
  font-size: 0.83rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--bright);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
}
.mc-desc {
  font-size: 0.76rem;
  color: var(--dim);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

.mc-num {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.2rem; right: 1.4rem;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  color: var(--rule);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}

/* ===== PDIA ===== */
.pdia-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--rule);
}
@media (max-width: 900px) { .pdia-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .pdia-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.pdia-card {
  background: var(--ink-2);
  padding: 2rem 1.8rem;
}
.pdia-letter {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 4rem;
  color: var(--fire);
  opacity: 0.18;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.pdia-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--bright);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.pdia-tagline {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  color: var(--fire);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.pdia-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
.pdia-list li {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--body);
  padding-left: 1.1rem;
  position: relative;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.pdia-list li::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.52em;
  width: 5px; height: 1px;
  background: var(--fire);
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* ===== QUESTIONS ===== */
.q-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--rule);
}
@media (max-width: 800px) { .q-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.q-card {
  background: var(--ink-2);
  padding: 1.8rem;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.q-card:hover { background: var(--ink-3); }
.q-id {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--fire);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.q-txt {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  color: var(--bright);
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  line-height: 1.45;
}
.q-why { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.65; }
.q-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 0.7rem;
  padding: 0.1rem 0.45rem;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.56rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.tag-b { background: rgba(74,143,245,0.1); color: #93c5fd; border: 1px solid rgba(74,143,245,0.2); }
.tag-m { background: rgba(155,116,232,0.1); color: #d8b4fe; border: 1px solid rgba(155,116,232,0.2); }
.tag-p { background: rgba(56,201,176,0.1); color: #6ee7b7; border: 1px solid rgba(56,201,176,0.2); }
.tag-g { background: rgba(255,87,51,0.1); color: #fca5a5; border: 1px solid rgba(255,87,51,0.2); }

/* ===== DIVIDER ===== */
.ruled { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); margin: 4rem 0; }

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
footer {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 2rem 5vw;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--mid);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* WHO ref */
.who-note {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--mid);
  margin-top: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="header-glow"></div>
  <div class="header-glow-2"></div>
  <div class="eyebrow">
    <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow-text">Intelligence Report · Data Analysis Unit · Punjab Smog Governance</span>
  </div>
  <h1>Lahore Air Quality<span class="year">2019 – 2023</span></h1>
  <p class="header-byline">PM2.5-based daily AQI monitoring paired with meteorological variables. Prepared for government briefing on Punjab smog governance and the PDIA framework.</p>
  <div class="meta-strip">
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="ml">Records</span><span class="mv">1,644 daily obs.</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="ml">Coverage</span><span class="mv">Jun 2019 – Nov 2023</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="ml">Pollutant</span><span class="mv">PM2.5 (AQI)</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item warn"><span class="ml">Missing AQI</span><span class="mv">221 days / 13.4%</span></div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

<!-- 01 KPIs -->
<section>
  <div class="sh">
    <div class="sh-num">01</div>
    <div class="sh-body">
      <div class="sh-title">At a Glance</div>
      <div class="sh-desc">Five-year summary of PM2.5-based AQI against WHO and Pakistan NEQS thresholds. The numbers are unambiguous: Lahore faces a structural, year-round air quality emergency.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="kpi-row">
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="kpi-lbl">5-Year Mean AQI</div>
      <div class="kpi-val">179</div>
      <div class="kpi-sub">PM2.5-based AQI</div>
      <span class="pill pill-r">Unhealthy</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="kpi-lbl">Peak Recorded</div>
      <div class="kpi-val">503</div>
      <div class="kpi-sub">Dec 26, 2021</div>
      <span class="pill pill-r">Hazardous</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="kpi-lbl">Days &ldquo;Good&rdquo; (AQI &le;50)</div>
      <div class="kpi-val">14</div>
      <div class="kpi-sub">of 1,423 measured</div>
      <span class="pill pill-g">Under 1%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="kpi-lbl">Hazardous Days</div>
      <div class="kpi-val">146</div>
      <div class="kpi-sub">AQI above 300</div>
      <span class="pill pill-p">10.3% of days</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="kpi-lbl">Worst Month (Avg)</div>
      <div class="kpi-val">Dec</div>
      <div class="kpi-sub">Avg AQI 314.9</div>
      <span class="pill pill-r">Very Unhealthy+</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="kpi-lbl">Missing AQI Days</div>
      <div class="kpi-val">221</div>
      <div class="kpi-sub">Gaps in record</div>
      <span class="pill pill-o">Data Gap</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 02 TIMESERIES -->
<section>
  <div class="sh">
    <div class="sh-num">02</div>
    <div class="sh-body">
      <div class="sh-title">Monthly AQI Trend</div>
      <div class="sh-desc">Monthly averages reveal a persistent smog crisis with dramatic winter spikes. WHO annual PM2.5 guideline corresponds to AQI approximately 22; Pakistan NEQS threshold is approximately AQI 100.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="alert">
    <strong>Data Completeness Warning:</strong> 2021 is missing 74 AQI readings (20% of the year) and 2022 is missing 115 (31.5% of the year). The 2022 peak average of AQI 198 may be an <em>underestimate</em>; sensors may have failed during the worst episodes.
  </div>

  <div class="chart-card">
    <div class="chart-hd">
      <h3>Monthly Average PM2.5 AQI (2019 – 2023)</h3>
      <p>Each point is a monthly average. Reference lines: WHO guideline (AQI 22) and Pakistan NEQS (AQI 100)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:320px">
      <canvas id="timeChart"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="who-note">Coloured dots indicate AQI category &nbsp;|&nbsp; Dashed lines mark WHO and NEQS thresholds</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 03 SEASONAL / YEARLY -->
<section>
  <div class="sh">
    <div class="sh-num">03</div>
    <div class="sh-body">
      <div class="sh-title">Seasonal and Annual Patterns</div>
      <div class="sh-desc">Winter months (October – February) drive the crisis. Monsoon (July – August) provides temporary relief through wind and rain. No consistent year-on-year improvement is visible.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="two-col" style="border:1px solid var(--rule)">
    <div class="chart-card" style="border:none">
      <div class="chart-hd">
        <h3>Average AQI by Month</h3>
        <p>5-year average. Smog season runs October through February.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:260px"><canvas id="seasonChart"></canvas></div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-card" style="border:none; border-left:1px solid var(--rule)">
      <div class="chart-hd">
        <h3>Year-on-Year Average and Peak AQI</h3>
        <p>2022 was the worst average year; 2021 holds the absolute peak reading.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:260px"><canvas id="yearChart"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 04 DISTRIBUTION -->
<section>
  <div class="sh">
    <div class="sh-num">04</div>
    <div class="sh-body">
      <div class="sh-title">AQI Category Distribution and Weather Correlations</div>
      <div class="sh-desc">Breakdown of valid AQI readings by EPA category, and Pearson correlations with meteorological variables. Wind and temperature are the dominant physical drivers.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="two-col" style="border:1px solid var(--rule)">
